# === Vercel (backend project → Settings → Environment Variables) ===
# Add the same variables above. MONGO_URI is REQUIRED — file storage cannot save on Vercel.
#
# MongoDB Atlas checklist:
# 1. Database Access → create user → copy password
# 2. Network Access → Add IP → Allow access from anywhere (0.0.0.0/0)
# 3. Connect → Drivers → copy connection string → replace <password>
#
# === Vercel (frontend project) ===
# VITE_API_URL=https://YOUR-BACKEND.vercel.app/api
